    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hey @thedevdavid, we made a component to replace `<InstantSearch>` rather than a provider to put at the top of the tree, as we need to inject a component in its children that waits for results to resume rendering of widgets (thanks to the new `use` function in React)\r\n\r\nDo you use InstantSearch in multiple pages ? Perhaps even somewhere in the layout, like for an autocomplete searchbox in a header ?\r\nWhat's in your `<SearchProvider>` exactly ? Asking these questions to understand better so we can give better documentation / features :D ",
