    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Do you use InstantSearch in multiple pages ? Perhaps even somewhere in the layout, like for an autocomplete searchbox in a header ? What's in your `<SearchProvider>` exactly ? Asking these questions to understand better so we can give better documentation / features :D\r\n\r\nSure. Thanks for listening! I did set up very vague and dirty example of what I want to achieve: https://codesandbox.io/p/sandbox/nostalgic-drake-p83fp6\r\n\r\nThe use case is that I want to have control over my layout and where to render widgets, refinements, results, autocomplete, etc. and I have searchbars on 2 routes. One on the search page, and another (an autocomplete) on the landing.\r\n\r\nHow would you solve this issue?\r\n",
